TITLE: Configuring Scala.js Build Settings
DESCRIPTION: Basic sbt build configuration for a Scala.js project, including plugin enablement and main module initialization.
SOURCE: https://github.com/scala-js/scala-js-website/blob/main/doc/tutorial/basic/index.md#2025-04-20_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: scala
CODE:
```
enablePlugins(ScalaJSPlugin)

name := "Scala.js Tutorial"
scalaVersion := "2.13.14"

// This is an application with a main method
scalaJSUseMainModuleInitializer := true
```

