TITLE: Enabling Scala.js Plugin in build.sbt
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to enable the Scala.js plugin in the build.sbt file. It creates a root project, enables the ScalaJSPlugin, and sets the scalaJSUseMainModuleInitializer setting for applications with a main method.
SOURCE: https://github.com/scala-js/scala-js-website/blob/main/doc/project/index.md#2025-04-20_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: scala
CODE:
```
lazy val root = project
  .in(file("."))
  .enablePlugins(ScalaJSPlugin)
  .settings(
    // for an application with a main method
    scalaJSUseMainModuleInitializer := true,
  )
```

