TITLE: Creating a Click Event Listener in Scala.js
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines a method in Scala.js that adds a message to the DOM when invoked, typically through a button click. It requires the 'scala.scalajs.js.annotation.JSExportTopLevel' annotation to make the method callable from JavaScript.
SOURCE: https://github.com/scala-js/scala-js-website/blob/main/doc/tutorial/basic/index.md#2025-04-20_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: scala
CODE:
```
