TITLE: Implementing a Data Item Renderer with Type-Specific Input Components in Laminar
DESCRIPTION: This method renders a table row for a data item, using specialized input components for different field types (string, double, int). It wires up each input to appropriate updater functions that transform the data item based on user input.
SOURCE: https://github.com/scala-js/scala-js-website/blob/main/doc/tutorial/laminar.md#2025-04-20_snippet_21

LANGUAGE: scala
