TITLE: Dynamic Module Loading Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Example demonstrating dynamic module loading functionality with a HeavyFeature class and MyApp implementation using js.dynamicImport.
SOURCE: https://github.com/scala-js/scala-js-website/blob/main/_posts/news/2021-01-12-announcing-scalajs-1.4.0.md#2025-04-20_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: scala
CODE:
```
class HeavyFeature {
  def doHeavyFeature(x: Int): Int =
    x * 2
}

class MyApp {
  def useHeavyFeature(): Unit = {
    val input: Int = getInput()
    val resultPromise: js.Promise[Int] = js.dynamicImport {
