SOURCE: https://github.com/scala-js/scala-js-website/blob/main/_posts/news/2015-01-23-announcing-scalajs-0.6.0-RC2.md#2025-04-20_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: scala
CODE:
```
scalaJSSemantics ~= (_.withRuntimeClassName { linkedClass =>
  val fullName = linkedClass.fullName
  if (fullName.startsWith("my.company.")) ""
  else fullName
})
```

