SOURCE: https://github.com/scala-js/scala-js-website/blob/main/_posts/news/2023-01-26-announcing-scalajs-1.13.0.md#2025-04-20_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: scala
CODE:
```
scalaJSLinkerConfig ~= {
  import org.scalajs.linker.interface.CheckedBehavior
  _.withSemantics(_
    .withNullPointers(CheckedBehavior.Unchecked)
  )
}
```

