TITLE: Warning Messages for JS Type Method Overrides (Text)
DESCRIPTION: Example compiler warnings that will be reported when attempting to override hashCode and equals in JS types starting in Scala.js 0.6.33. The warnings explain that these overrides don't affect the actual behavior.
