TITLE: Desugaring Implicit Constructor Invocation in Scala.js
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how the Scala compiler desugars the implicit usage of 'js.ConstructorTag'. The manual version of calling the constructor cannot be written in user code since the constructor of 'js.ConstructorTag' is private.
