TITLE: Configuring String Index Out of Bounds Behavior in Scala.js
DESCRIPTION: Configuration snippet to enable compliant StringIndexOutOfBoundsException behavior in the Scala.js linker. This setting makes string index exceptions behave the same as on the JVM in both fastLink and fullLink modes.
